variable.name: Lifetime nosebleed
variable.description: How many spontaneous (that seem to happen for no reason) nosebleeds would you estimate you have had in your entire life?

variable.name: Comparative bleeding
variable.description: Compared to other people, when you get a minor cut or nose bleed, do you think that you bleed less, about the same, or more? Please consider the amount of bleeding and the length of time you bleed.

variable.name: Spontaneous Bruising
variable.description: How often do you bruise without trauma or injury? In other words, how often do you get bruises that seem to happen for no reason?

variable.name: Gum Bleeding
variable.description: When you brush your teeth how often do you notice bleeding from your gums?

variable.name: Tooth extraction
variable.description: Have you ever had a tooth extracted (pulled out) or any other dental surgery?

variable.name: Bleeding with Tooth extraction
variable.description: When you had your tooth pulled (or had other dental surgery), did you have a problem with too much bleeding?

variable.name: Bleeding treatment with Tooth extraction
variable.description: When you had your tooth pulled (or had other dental surgery), did your doctor or you have to do something to stop the bleeding?

variable.name: Surgery
variable.description: Have you ever had surgery or any other operation not including dental surgery?

variable.name: Bleeding with Surgery
variable.description: Have you ever had problems with bleeding following any surgery?

variable.name: Bleeding treatment with surgery
variable.description: Has your doctor or you ever had to do something to stop bleeding after surgery?

variable.name: Bleeding treatment, non-surgical
variable.description: Have you ever had medical treatment to stop bleeding that was not associated with surgery? This includes incidents when you may have injured yourself, received vaccinations or injections, or had any part of your body pierced.

variable.name: Comparative dental bleeding
variable.description: When you go to the dentist, about how much do you bleed from your gums? Would you say it is more, about the same, or less than most people your age?

variable.name: Menarche
variable.description: At what age did you have your first period?

variable.description: On average, how many days do your periods last?

variable.description: Do you use hormonal birth control (pill, patch, ring, or shot)?
